      <title>hexo 搭建博客</title>
      <link href="2021/01/25/17043/0/"/>
      <url>2021/01/25/17043/0/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="引言"><a href="#引言" class="headerlink" title="引言"></a>引言</h1><blockquote><p>hexo 搭建博客</p></blockquote><a id="more"></a><h1 id="相关依赖"><a href="#相关依赖" class="headerlink" title="相关依赖"></a>相关依赖</h1><h2 id="Node-js"><a href="#Node-js" class="headerlink" title="Node.js"></a>Node.js</h2><p>Node.js 安装见相关文档</p><h2 id="hexo"><a href="#hexo" class="headerlink" title="hexo"></a>hexo</h2><h3 id="hexo-官网"><a href="#hexo-官网" class="headerlink" title="hexo 官网"></a>hexo 官网</h3><p>hexo 官网 <a href="https://hexo.io/">https://hexo.io/</a></p><p>hexo 中文官网 <a href="https://hexo.io/zh-cn/">https://hexo.io/zh-cn/</a></p><p>hexo 详细使用见官网</p><h3 id="安装-hexo"><a href="#安装-hexo" class="headerlink" title="安装 hexo"></a>安装 hexo</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ npm install -g hexo</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h1 id="建站"><a href="#建站" class="headerlink" title="建站"></a>建站</h1><h2 id="初始化-hexo"><a href="#初始化-hexo" class="headerlink" title="初始化 hexo"></a>初始化 hexo</h2><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ hexo init</span><br><span class="line">$ npm install</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="启动-hexo"><a href="#启动-hexo" class="headerlink" title="启动 hexo"></a>启动 hexo</h2><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ hexo server</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>启动成功访问 <a href="http://localhost:4000/">http://localhost:4000</a> 如下图<br><img src="/2021/01/25/17043/0/runsuccess.png" alt="启动成功"></p><h1 id="配置"><a href="#配置" class="headerlink" title="配置"></a>配置</h1><h2 id="更改主题"><a href="#更改主题" class="headerlink" title="更改主题"></a>更改主题</h2><p>配置 hexo-theme-next 主题</p><p>git 地址 <a href="https://github.com/theme-next/hexo-theme-next">https://github.com/theme-next/hexo-theme-next</a></p><p>选择相应版本代码下载 zip 到本地，本文使用 7.8.0 版本</p><p>安装有两种方式，一种直接 github 克隆项目，方便版本升级，一种直接下载文件，本文选择直接下载，因为需要修改源代码，克隆意义不大。</p><p>解压下载的 zip 将文件拷贝到项目的 themes 文件夹中，并重命名文件为 next，如图</p><p><img src="/2021/01/25/17043/0/nextdir.png" alt="next 目录"></p><p>修改项目 _config.yml</p><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">theme:</span> <span class="string">next</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="主题配置文件选择"><a href="#主题配置文件选择" class="headerlink" title="主题配置文件选择"></a>主题配置文件选择</h2><p>配置文件有两个，一个是项目的 _config.yml，一个是主题的 _config.yml。</p><p>Hexo 5.0.0 起提供独立的 _config.[theme].yml 文件的方式，但是不支持热部署。</p><p>next 主题也提供了两个解决方案，可以参见next包中的 docs/zh-CN/DATA-FILES.md 中文文档，同样不支持热部署。</p><p>选择 _config.[theme].yml 方式在根目录建 _config.next.yml 文件</p><h2 id="永久链接配置"><a href="#永久链接配置" class="headerlink" title="永久链接配置"></a>永久链接配置</h2><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install hexo-abbrlink --save</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h1 id="图片相对路径问题"><a href="#图片相对路径问题" class="headerlink" title="图片相对路径问题"></a>图片相对路径问题</h1><p>修改配置</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install https://github.com/7ym0n/hexo-asset-image --save</span><br><span class="line">有 bug</span><br><span class="line">npm install hexo-asset-image --save</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">post_asset_folder:</span> <span class="literal">true</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h1 id="首页不显示全文"><a href="#首页不显示全文" class="headerlink" title="首页不显示全文"></a>首页不显示全文</h1><p>在文章的要分段的地方加上下面注释</p><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;!-- more --&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h1 id="标签位置放到标题下方"><a href="#标签位置放到标题下方" class="headerlink" title="标签位置放到标题下方"></a>标签位置放到标题下方</h1><p>next 主题文件夹下 layout/_macro/post.swig</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&#123;%- if post.categories and post.categories.length and theme.post_meta.categories %&#125;</span><br><span class="line">  &lt;span class&#x3D;&quot;post-meta-item&quot;&gt;</span><br><span class="line">    &lt;span class&#x3D;&quot;post-meta-item-icon&quot;&gt;</span><br><span class="line">      &lt;i class&#x3D;&quot;fa fa-folder-o&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;i&gt;</span><br><span class="line">    &lt;&#x2F;span&gt;</span><br><span class="line">    &lt;span class&#x3D;&quot;post-meta-item-text&quot;&gt;&#123;&#123; __(&#39;post.in&#39;) &#125;&#125;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;</span><br><span class="line">    &#123;%- for cat in post.categories.toArray() %&#125;</span><br><span class="line">      &lt;span itemprop&#x3D;&quot;about&quot; itemscope itemtype&#x3D;&quot;http:&#x2F;&#x2F;schema.org&#x2F;Thing&quot;&gt;</span><br><span class="line">        &lt;a href&#x3D;&quot;&#123;&#123; url_for(cat.path) &#125;&#125;&quot; itemprop&#x3D;&quot;url&quot; rel&#x3D;&quot;index&quot;&gt;&lt;span itemprop&#x3D;&quot;name&quot;&gt;&#123;&#123; cat.name &#125;&#125;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;&#x2F;a&gt;</span><br><span class="line">      &lt;&#x2F;span&gt;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">      &#123;%- set cat_length &#x3D; post.categories.length %&#125;</span><br><span class="line">      &#123;%- if cat_length &gt; 1 and loop.index !&#x3D;&#x3D; cat_length %&#125;</span><br><span class="line">        &#123;&#123; __(&#39;symbol.comma&#39;) &#125;&#125;</span><br><span class="line">      &#123;%- endif %&#125;</span><br><span class="line">    &#123;%- endfor %&#125;</span><br><span class="line">  &lt;&#x2F;span&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&#123;%- endif %&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>下方增加</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;!-- 标签位置放到标题下方 --&gt;</span><br><span class="line">          &#123;%- if post.tags and post.tags.length and theme.post_meta.tags %&#125;</span><br><span class="line">            &lt;span class&#x3D;&quot;post-meta-item&quot;&gt;</span><br><span class="line">              &lt;span class&#x3D;&quot;post-meta-item-icon&quot;&gt;</span><br><span class="line">                &lt;i class&#x3D;&quot;fa fa-tag&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;i&gt;</span><br><span class="line">              &lt;&#x2F;span&gt;</span><br><span class="line">              &lt;span class&#x3D;&quot;post-meta-item-text&quot;&gt;&#123;&#123; __(&#39;menu.tags&#39;) &#125;&#125;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;</span><br><span class="line">              &#123;%- for cat in post.tags.toArray() %&#125;</span><br><span class="line">                &lt;span itemprop&#x3D;&quot;about&quot; itemscope itemtype&#x3D;&quot;http:&#x2F;&#x2F;schema.org&#x2F;Thing&quot;&gt;</span><br><span class="line">                  &lt;a href&#x3D;&quot;&#123;&#123; url_for(cat.path) &#125;&#125;&quot; itemprop&#x3D;&quot;url&quot; rel&#x3D;&quot;index&quot;&gt;&lt;span itemprop&#x3D;&quot;name&quot;&gt;&#123;&#123; cat.name &#125;&#125;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;&#x2F;a&gt;</span><br><span class="line">                &lt;&#x2F;span&gt;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">                &#123;%- set cat_length &#x3D; post.tags.length %&#125;</span><br><span class="line">                &#123;%- if cat_length &gt; 1 and loop.index !&#x3D;&#x3D; cat_length %&#125;</span><br><span class="line">                  &#123;&#123; __(&#39;symbol.comma&#39;) &#125;&#125;</span><br><span class="line">                &#123;%- endif %&#125;</span><br><span class="line">              &#123;%- endfor %&#125;</span><br><span class="line">            &lt;&#x2F;span&gt;</span><br><span class="line">          &#123;%- endif %&#125;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;!-- 标签位置放到标题下方 --&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>主题配置文件增加</p><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">post_meta:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">tags:</span> <span class="literal">true</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>删掉底部标签</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&#123;%- if post.tags and post.tags.length %&#125;</span><br><span class="line">  &#123;%- if theme.tag_icon %&#125;</span><br><span class="line">    &#123;%- set tag_indicate &#x3D; &#39;&lt;i class&#x3D;&quot;fa fa-tag&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;i&gt;&#39; %&#125;</span><br><span class="line">  &#123;% else %&#125;</span><br><span class="line">    &#123;%- set tag_indicate &#x3D; &#39;#&#39; %&#125;</span><br><span class="line">  &#123;%- endif %&#125;</span><br><span class="line">  &lt;div class&#x3D;&quot;post-tags&quot;&gt;</span><br><span class="line">    &#123;%- for tag in post.tags.toArray() %&#125;</span><br><span class="line">      &lt;a href&#x3D;&quot;&#123;&#123; url_for(tag.path) &#125;&#125;&quot; rel&#x3D;&quot;tag&quot;&gt;&#123;&#123; tag_indicate &#125;&#125; &#123;&#123; tag.name &#125;&#125;&lt;&#x2F;a&gt;</span><br><span class="line">    &#123;%- endfor %&#125;</span><br><span class="line">  &lt;&#x2F;div&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&#123;%- endif %&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h1 id="配置自动推送-git"><a href="#配置自动推送-git" class="headerlink" title="配置自动推送 git"></a>配置自动推送 git</h1><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ npm install hexo-deployer-git --save</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">deploy:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">type:</span> <span class="string">git</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">repository:</span> <span class="string">https://github.com/baidongbin/baidongbin.github.io</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">branch:</span> <span class="string">master</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>安装 pm2</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install -g pm2</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>安装</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install -g github-webhook-handler</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h1 id="本地搜索"><a href="#本地搜索" class="headerlink" title="本地搜索"></a>本地搜索</h1><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install hexo-generator-search --save</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
      
      
